				<td colspan="2"><span>So I have spent a bunch of time trolling thorught the boards, and have read many great ideas of places to swarm. Now seeing as I am almost level 58 it is rather embarrassing for me to ask the question: &quot;What is swarming exactly?&quot; Okay so it sounds like you grab a bunch of mobs and drop them rather quickly. It sounds simple, but I was looking through my spell book and was noticing a lack of higher level AoE songs, which I pressume are what one would play when swarming. [Please excuse the rambling, I am only going on about what I have assumed as swarming to make up for my ignorance of actul swarming techniques]</span></td>
