			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Toggling between targets used to work with tab automatically, but does not any more. You can, under keyboard - options, set any key to toggle between your last two targets. 
<br />

<br />
I use &quot;a&quot; because I long ago turned auto-attack onto the ~ key, but you can do whatever is convenient. This toggling key is not only crucial for any sort of pet related work, but also for crowd control. Point and click simply is not an efficient way to get pair of adds under control. Alas, you get three or more, you'll have no choice ...
<br />

<br />
Good luck.
<br />

<br />
Rivyn. </span></td>
