			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>To break charm, do not rely on hide, it is capped way too low to work more than 25% of the time and you don't want to get exp on 25% of your swarm kite pets, lol.  Twisting in your wind instrument and casting 29(?) invis is the best way to go, unless you can get one of the many highly prized click invis items.  At 51, you can do what I do, and that is to use Travel song to break invis, but that has problems in and of itself.  It cancels selos, so you need to recast selos afterwards, leaving you running at a snails pace until selos kicks in, which can mean death if your swarm catches you (if you get a lag spike at the same time you lose selos, ouch).  Run 3 helps tremendously here, I've never been caught this way and it works for me.  Do whatever works for you, but don't rely on hide.
<br />

<br />
Sinfonian</span></td>
